name: The beginning of an era
description:
It all started with a guy accepting bitcoin as payment for a pizza, that was the story that caught my attention to the crypto world, I started my research, made some friends and one of them gave me 1 ETH valued $15 at the time, saved and sold it time later for $200 because I needed the money, but I did not end there, because years later i'm here, minting my first NFT as pizza and crypto lover, this one means a lot to me, I'm here for the freedom, I'm here for the community, I'm here because I'm not an artist but I made this draw, and this is mine, but It can be yours too if you want to do more than just right-click save.

5 copies, one for me, one for sale, two for people I care when they join me in this ride and the last one for the future.

October, 2021. First mint.
